# AMOL 支払方法・決済画面 改修引き継ぎ README

最終更新: 2026-05-02  
対象: `frontend/amol` / `backend/internal/platform/di` / `backend/internal/adapters/out/stripe` / `backend/internal/adapters/out/firestore/paymentMethod`

